quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"Ggule$ s wass n tnekra!"
  75,2,"Ggule$ s yiman bu tuzzma!"
  75,3,"Aâni i$il umdan, i$san is, ur ten Nessemlili ara?"
  75,4,"Xaîi! Nezmer a Nesserked iduren is."
  75,5,"Maca, ib$a umdan ad irnu di tucmitin."
  75,6,"Isteqsay anda t wass n tnekra."
  75,7,"Ma tullsent wallen,"
  75,8,"u i$ab waggur,"
  75,9,"u iîij akked waggur pwazdin;"
  75,10,"assen, amdan ad yini: ""tarewla sani""?"
  75,11,"Xaîi! Ssôan ur illi."
  75,12,"Axxam ippuôe$ben, ar Mass ik, ass nni."
  75,13,"Assen, ad ippuxebbeô umdan $ef wayen ibbwi ar zdat, akked wayen irra ar deffir."
  75,14,"Ih, amdan, deg iman is, ad iwali."
  75,15,"Xas issuter ssmaê."
  75,16,"Ur pêerrik, yis, iles ik, a d t$iwlev yis."
  75,17,"Fella£ ajemmel is akked t$uôi s."
  75,18,"Mara t N$eô, ihi, ssel i t$uôi s."
  75,19,"Sinna, ih, fella£ abeggen is."
  75,20,"Xaîi! Wanag têemmlem taêemmaqt."
  75,21,"Di laxeôt, testehzayem."
  75,22,"Udmawen, assen, ad feooeoen."
  75,23,"Ar Mass nnsen, ad pmuqulen."
  75,24,"Udmawen, assen, ad neééfen."
  75,25,"Ëûan, i twa$it ad ppunefken."
  75,26,"Xaîi! Mi tuli ar irawen,"
  75,27,"ad inin: ""anwa ay d agezzan""?"
  75,28,"U iêûa ar wagi d lefôaq."
  75,29,"Imlal ufud ar ufud."
  75,30,"Ar Mass ik, assen, tanheôt."
  75,31,"Ur iumin, ur ipéalla;"
  75,32,"U irna inkeô, iwexxeô."
  75,33,"Sinna, ar twacult is irra s pnefxa."
  75,34,"A lwexda k, a lwexda!"
  75,35,"D$a, a lwexda k, a lwexda!"
  75,36,"Aâni i$il umdan d ilelli i ippuserreê?"
  75,37,"Aâni ur illi d tiqqit iuzlen n l$ella?"
  75,38,"Sinna, iu$al d argen. D$a Ixleq, Imsel."
  75,39,"Irra segs tayuga, ddkeô akked nnta."
  75,40,"Aâni Wa ur Izmir a d Issider lmeggtin?"
